st lawrenc seaway to open on schedul the st lawrenc seaway and the welland canal link lake eri and ontario were expect to open as schedul on march 31 and april 1 , respect , a st lawrenc seaway offici said . the entir seaway is alreadi free of ice due to the mild winter and could be open for navig today , `` but there doe n't seem to be enough demand from ship compani to warrant an earli open , '' the canadian offici said . repair are continu at a step up pace on the welland canal and should be complet by the april 1 start-up date , she ad .